title: Ebro In The Morning - House Music Is Back.
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/21/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing Drake's new album 'Honestly, Nevermind', and Beyonce's latest single! Plus HOUSE MUSIC IS BACK! Let the gurus cleanse the air and solve your problems!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
